bike.description: Fully Heat Treated Post Welding Quadangle Frame Design, Mid BB, Ovalized & Tapered Chain & Seat Stays, Sealed Integrated Headset, 5mm Thick Dropouts, Integrated Seat Clamp, 14mm Frame Dropouts with 3/8" Adapters, Cutout Seat Tube for Large Tire Clearance, Externally Machined 73mm Wide Mid Bottom Bracket, Externally Machined Campy Compatible Integrated Headset, Includes Heat Treated & Butted Aftermarket Cr-Mo Landing Gear Forks & Tange Sealed, Integrated Headset, Sizes: S (47cm), M (51cm), L (56cm), and Weight 6.8 lbs Frame (51cm)
